@startuml sd_DepartmentService_create
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title DepartmentService.create(department) - 创建部门

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "DepartmentController" as Ctrl
participant "DepartmentService" as Service
participant "DepartmentRepository" as Repo
participant "Department\n(实体)" as Entity

Client -> Ctrl: POST /api/departments\n{name, code, parentId, ...}
Ctrl -> Service: create(department)
note right of Service : @Transactional
Service -> Repo: save(department)
Repo --> Service: 持久化后的Department\n(含ID)
Service --> Ctrl: Department
note right of Entity : JPA自动生成ID\n维护parent关系
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<Department>
@enduml
